data.description: This absolutely adorable 2 bedroom, 2 full bathroom single will surely steal your heart! The home exudes curb appeal with is covered front porch that spans the front of the home and the professionally hardscaped mulch beds. Enter through the front door into the large tiled foyer featuring wainscotting and a half wall to the spacious living room. The living room offers luxury vinyl plank flooring, wainscoting, ceiling fan, gas fireplace, octagonal decorative window, and a tiled landing at the bottom of the stairs. The dining room features gorgeous hardwood flooring, a window bench, chair rail, French doors to sunroom, and provides an open concept to the 26-handle kitchen. The kitchen is equipped with tile flooring, tile backsplash, display cabinetry, all new lighting, large island, and a deep sink. A full bathroom just off the dining room is centrally located for convenience and is complete with newer luxury vinyl plank flooring and a stall shower. Finishing the first floor is the bright sunroom, also offering newer LVP, ceiling fan, and a glass slider to rear, two tier, wooden deck and the private, rear yard with fire pit and vinyl privacy fencing. The second floor provides two generously sized bedrooms, both with luxury vinyl plank flooring and ample closet space, the primary bedroom features a private bathroom! The unfinished basement houses the gas-fueled mechanicals, laundry connections, and offers plenty of storage. Brand new Gas furnace and Central A/C just installed in March of 2023. A non-paved driveway to the right of the home provides off-street parking for two cars! What more could you be searching for? This starter home is move-in ready and waiting for you! Call today for your private showing.
